OL,3,CPatients told to visit other emergency
OL,4,Cdepartments amid hospital power outage
OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fat Surrey and Sussex Healthcare NHS
OL,8,FTrust following a power failure at one
OL,9,Fof its hospitals.
OL,11,FThe outage is affecting the Intensive
OL,12,FCare Unit and High Dependency Unit at
OL,13,FEast Surrey Hospital.
OL,15,FThe hospital has evacuated both units,
OL,16,Fwith the families of patients
OL,17,Fcontacted.
