OL,3,CPatients told to visit other emergency
OL,4,Cdepartments amid hospital power outage
OL,6,FAnyone with an elective procedure on
OL,7,FTuesday 20 February 2024 at East
OL,8,FSurrey Hospital will be contacted, as
OL,9,Fit might need to be rescheduled.
OL,11,FOutpatients are being told to still go
OL,12,Fto their appointments unless they have
OL,13,Fbeen contacted to reschedule.
OL,15,FThe NHS Trust is asking members of the
OL,16,Fpublic to consider going to
OL,17,Falternative Emergency Departments if
OL,18,Ftheir condition isn't life-
OL,19,Fthreatening, in order to reduce the
OL,20,Fpressure on intensive care services.
