OL,3,CPatients told to visit other emergency
OL,4,Cdepartments amid hospital power outage
OL,6,FThe nearest Urgent Treatment Centres
OL,7,Fand Minor Injury Units include
OL,8,FCaterham, Horsham, Crawley and East
OL,9,FGrinstead.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Surrey and Sussex
OL,12,FHealthcare NHS Trust said: "We are
OL,13,Fworking to urgently resolve the power
OL,14,Fissues in our Intensive Care and High
OL,15,FDependency Units and ensure the safe
OL,16,Fcare of all those who need our
OL,17,Fservices.
