OL,6,F"While our Emergency Department
OL,7,Fremains open, we are asking members of
OL,8,Fthe public to please consider other
OL,9,Flocal alternatives to ED - including
OL,10,Fnearby treatment centres at Crawley,
OL,11,FCaterham Dene, Horsham and East
OL,12,FGrinstead if your condition is not
OL,13,Flife-threatening. This will reduce the
OL,14,Fpotential pressure on our intensive
OL,15,Fcare services and ensure care is
OL,16,Favailable to patients who need it
OL,17,Fmost."
